item.description:

You dont’ need any of these running.

C:\PROGRA~1\COMMON~1\AOL\ACS\AOLacsd.exe - Crap AOL stuff
C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_06\bin\jusched.exe - Java Update
C:\Program Files\CyberLink\PowerDVD\DVDLauncher.exe - Power DVD updater/launcher
C:\Program Files\Musicmatch\Musicmatch Jukebox\mm_tray.exe - Don’t need it running
C:\Program Files\Musicmatch\Musicmatch Jukebox\mmtask.exe - Don’t need it running
C:\Program Files\Common Files\AOL\1144768289\ee\AOLSoftware.exe - Crap AOL software again
C:\Program Files\Common Files\Real\Update_OB\realsched.exe - Real updater
C:\Program Files\QuickTime\qttask.exe - Don’t need it running
C:\Program Files\Messenger\msmsgs.exe - Don’t need it running
C:\DOCUME~1\Josh\MYDOCU~1\MBOLS~1\ati2evxx.exe - WTF is this?
c:\program files\common files\aol\1144768289\ee\aim6.exe - Don’t need it running

You can turn these off from loading in Spybot > Tools > System Startup

~Ron
